  "prompt": "I am going to organising an party, for that I need to clean my home on or before 31/12/2017. So suggest me cleaning service company in Perth?",
  "response": "Here are a few cleaning service companies in Perth that you might consider for your home cleaning needs:\n\n1. **Fantastic Cleaners Perth** - They offer a range of cleaning services including end-of-lease cleaning, house cleaning, and more.\n\n2. **Perth Home Cleaners** - They provide residential cleaning services tailored to your needs, whether it's a one-time clean or regular maintenance.\n\n3. **G\u2019day Cleaning** - Known for their professional cleaning services, they offer domestic cleaning and can accommodate special requests.\n\n4. **Clean & Tidy** - This company focuses on environmentally friendly cleaning solutions, ensuring a thorough clean without harsh chemicals.\n\n5. **Jim's Cleaning** - A well-known name in Australia, they provide a wide range of cleaning services and have a strong reputation for quality.\n\nMake sure to check their reviews, availability, and pricing to find the best fit for your needs. It\u2019s also a good idea to contact them ahead of time to ensure they can meet your deadline of cleaning before your party.",
